label: A4B_cP5_221_bc_a-001
title: {\em Erroneous} $L'1_{0}$ Structure
comments:
We (Hicks, 2019) accidentally misplaced the nickel atom in the $L'1_{0}$ structure.  The correct structure can be found at \href{current_web_home_dir/A4B_cP5_221_ac_b-002}{$\gamma$'-Fe$_{4}$N $L'1_{0}$ page}. 
 Despite our error, this is a binary form of the \href{current_web_home_dir/AB3C_cP5_221_a_c_b-001}{cubic perovskite structure (AB3C\_cP5\_221\_a\_c\_b)}, {\em Strukturbericht} designation $E2_{1}$.
